headline: PPG enters new era with Tasca Racing as Austin Prock takes the wheel
summary: STRONGSVILLE, Ohio, February 25, 2026--PPG (NYSE: PPG) today announced its 2026 NATIONAL HOT ROD ASSOCIATION® (NHRA®) Mission Foods Drag Racing Series primary race schedule with Tasca Racing. The season marks a new era for the partnership as two‑time and reigning NHRA Funny Car world champion Austin Prock will drive the PPG NITRO MUSTANG DARK HORSE® Funny Car, following Tasca Racing’s recently announced driver lineup changes.
